description: Mister FruitCup offers a medley of fresh mouth watering fruit cups inspired by the popular Mexican street-food snack. Mister FruitCup is Austin’s only choice for the best fruit cups your palate will ever experience because they are made to order daily.Whether they’re dressed with a tasty sauce, homemade whipping cream, or fresh herbs, these fruit cups are sure to be a crowd pleaser.  They are perfect for lunch, snacks or on-the-go!
name: Mister FruitCup
